title: Pokemon Scarlet and Violet Release Date! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 06.01.22
description:
Greg and Janet react to the new Pokemon Scarlet and Violet trailer, talk Horizon: Call of the Mountain, and more!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:08:00- Housekeeping
Gamescast is LIVE right after this on patreon.com/kindafunnygames! Tim and Bless are reacting to Sonic Frontiers, we’re talking MORE Pokemon, and predicting SGF!
PSILY is LIVE tomorrow after State of Play reactions!

Gordon McGuire & Fargo Brady
The Roper Report  -
00:11:08 - Pokemon Scarlet and Violet Release Date!

0:37:20 - Your PlayStation Plus Monthly Games for June

Variety’s Joe Otterson

00:51:10 - It’s Pride Month, so be like Vince Zampella! Ethan Gatch at Kotaku
00:55:45 -Tekken 7 Sells Well, GIB
00:55:56 - John Madden is on the cover of Madden 23
